      <scopecontent id="aspace_cfdac2ab80039fa81e6cd6d3634862e8">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The papers consist of diaries, memorabilia, printed materials, and photographs of R. Emms, a noncommissioned officer in the British Army, Company E, 2nd Batallion, Norfolk Regiment, during the Boer War in South Africa. In his diaries and sketches, Emms recounts army life and battles in which he participated. The photographs are primarily of the Norfolk Regiment encampment and soldiers.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
